msgstr ""
"Ostotilauksia käytetään saapuvien tuotteiden ja tuotepakkausten "
"vastaanottotapahtumien käsittelyyn varastossa. Luo ensin tarjouspyyntö ja "
"vahvista se luodaksesi |PO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:61
msgid ":doc:`../../purchase/manage_deals/rfq`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../purchase/manage_deals/rfq`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:63
msgid ""
"To process and scan barcodes for warehouse receipts, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Barcode` app."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:65
msgid ""
"Once inside the **Barcode** app, a :guilabel:`Barcode Scanning` screen "
"displaying different options is presented."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:71
msgid ""
"To process receipts, click the :guilabel:`Operations` button at the bottom "
"of the screen. The :guilabel:`Operations` overview page opens."
msgstr ""
"Käsittele vastaanotot napsauttamalla :guilabel:`Toiminnot`-painiketta näytön "
