#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:150
msgid ""
"In the **Barcode** app, a :guilabel:`Barcode Scanning` screen displaying "
"different options opens. To process deliveries, click "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` button at the bottom of the screen. This opens "
