#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:253
msgid ""
"An *export document*, required by customs to ship packages from one country "
"to another, can be automatically printed in Odoo by following these steps:"
msgstr ""
"*Vientiasiakirja*, joka vaaditaan tullissa pakettien lähettämiseen maasta "
"toiseen, voidaan tulostaa automaattisesti Odossa seuraavasti:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:256
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Export Documents` checkbox in the :ref:`operation type "
"settings <inventory/shipping_receiving/print_setup>`."
msgstr ""
"Valitse :guilabel:`Export Documents` -valintaruutu :ref:`toimintotyypin "
"asetuksissa <inventory/shipping_receiving/print_setup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:259
msgid "Assign the export document to the printer."
msgstr "Määritä vientiasiakirja tulostimelle."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:264
msgid ""
"Similar to the :ref:`printer assignment instructions for carrier labels "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/assign-printer>`, after connecting a "
"compatible printer to the Odoo *IoT* app, go to :menuselection:`IoT app --> "
"Devices`, and select the desired printer."
msgstr ""
"Samoin kuin :ref:`tulostimen määritysohjeet rahtikirjoille <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/assign-printer>`, kun yhteensopiva tulostin on yhdistetty "
"Odoon *IoT*-sovellukseen, siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`IoT app --> "
"Devices` ja valitse haluamasi tulostin."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:268
msgid ""
"In the printer configuration form, go to the :guilabel:`Printer Reports` "
"tab, and click :guilabel:`Add a line`. In the :guilabel:`Add: Reports` pop-"
"up window that appears, add the :guilabel:`Shipping Documents` report to "
"assign the export document to the printer."
msgstr ""
"Tulostimen asetuslomaakkeella siirry välilehdelle :guilabel:`Printer "
"Reports` ja napsauta :guilabel:`Add a line`. Näkyviin tulevassa "
":guilabel:`Add: Reports` -ponnahdusikkunassa lisää :guilabel:`Shipping "
"Documents` -raportti määrittääksesi vientiasiakirjan tulostimelle."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:0
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:278
msgid "Export document for a shipment from the USA to Belgium."
msgstr "Vientiasiakirja lähetykselle Yhdysvalloista Belgiaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:283
msgid "Package content"
msgstr "Paketin sisältö"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:285
msgid ""
"A *package content* PDF includes the package's barcode, packed date, along "
"with a list of contained products and quantities."
msgstr ""
"*Paketin sisältö* -PDF sisältää paketin viivakoodin, pakkauspäivämäärän sekä "
"luettelon pakkauksessa olevista tuotteista ja määristä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:288
msgid ""
"To print this form automatically, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Operation Types`, and select the desired operation type. "
"Then, go to the :guilabel:`Hardware` tab, and tick the :guilabel:`Package "
"Contents` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Tulostaaksesi tämän lomakkeen automaattisesti siirry kohtaan "
":menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Operation Types` ja "
"valitse haluamasi toimintotyyppi. Siirry sitten välilehdelle "
":guilabel:`Hardware` ja valitse :guilabel:`Package Contents` -valintaruutu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:293
msgid ""
"If the option is not available, enable the :doc:`Packages <../../"
"product_management/configure/package>` feature, by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`, ticking "
"the :guilabel:`Packages` checkbox, and clicking :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Jos vaihtoehto ei ole käytettävissä, ota :doc:`Packages <../../"
"product_management/configure/package>` -ominaisuus käyttöön siirtymällä "
"kohtaan :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"valitsemalla :guilabel:`Packages` -valintaruutu ja napsauttamalla "
":guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:298
msgid ""
"After enabling the feature in the :guilabel:`Hardware` tab, validating the "
"operation prints a PDF of the package contents."
msgstr ""
"Kun ominaisuus on otettu käyttöön :guilabel:`Hardware` -välilehdellä, "
"toiminnon vahvistaminen tulostaa PDF-tiedoston paketin sisällöstä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:0
msgid ""
"Package contents form showing the package contents, barcode, and pack date."
msgstr ""
"Paketin sisältölomake, jossa näkyy paketin sisältö, viivakoodi ja "
"pakkauspäivämäärä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:307
msgid "Package contents showing the package contents, barcode, and pack date."
msgstr ""
"Paketin sisältö, jossa näkyy paketin sisältö, viivakoodi ja "
"pakkauspäivämäärä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:312
msgid "Package label"
msgstr "Pakettitarra"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:314
msgid ""
"A *package label* that shows the package's barcode and pack date can be "
"configured to print upon clicking the *Put in Pack* button."
msgstr ""
"*Pakettitarra*, jossa näkyy paketin viivakoodi ja pakkauspäivämäärä, voidaan "
"määrittää tulostumaan *Put in Pack* -painiketta napsautettaessa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:318
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Put in Pack` button is available **only** when "
"the :doc:`Packages <../../product_management/configure/package>` feature is "
"enabled in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Put in Pack` -painike on käytettävissä **vain**, kun "
":doc:`Packages <../../product_management/configure/package>` -ominaisuus on "
"käytössä kohdassa :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:322
msgid ""
"After it is enabled, the :guilabel:`Put in Pack` button is available on all "
"inventory operations (e.g. receipt, pickings, internal transfers, delivery "
"orders, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Kun se on otettu käyttöön, :guilabel:`Put in Pack` -painike on käytettävissä "
"kaikissa varastotoiminnoissa (esim. vastaanotto, keräily, sisäiset siirrot, "
"toimitustilaukset jne.)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:325
msgid ""
"To automatically print the package label when the :guilabel:`Put in Pack` "
"button is clicked, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Operation Types`. Select the desired operation type, and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Package Label` checkbox in the :guilabel:`Hardware` tab. "
"Labels can be printed in :guilabel:`PDF` or :guilabel:`ZPL` file formats, as "
"defined in the :guilabel:`Print label as` field."
msgstr ""
"Tulostaaksesi pakettitarran automaattisesti, kun :guilabel:`Put in Pack` -"
"painiketta napsautetaan, siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Operation Types`. Valitse haluamasi toimintotyyppi ja "
"valitse :guilabel:`Package Label` -valintaruutu :guilabel:`Hardware` -"
"välilehdellä. Tarrat voidaan tulostaa :guilabel:`PDF`- tai :guilabel:`ZPL` -"
"tiedostomuodoissa :guilabel:`Print label as` -kentässä määritetyn mukaisesti."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:0
msgid "PDF of package barcode and package date."
msgstr "PDF paketin viivakoodista ja pakkauspäivämäärästä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:3
msgid "Sendcloud integration"
msgstr "Sendcloud-integraatio"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:5
msgid ""
"Sendcloud is a shipping service aggregator that facilitates the integration "
"of European shipping carriers with Odoo. Once integrated, users can select "
"shipping carriers on inventory operations in their Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Sendcloud on lähetyspalveluiden yhdistäjä, joka helpottaa eurooppalaisten "
"kuljetusyhtiöiden integrointia Odoon. Integroinnin jälkeen käyttäjät voivat "
"valita kuljetusyhtiöitä varastotoiminnoissa Odoo-tietokannassaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:10
msgid "Setup in Sendcloud"
msgstr "Sendcloudin asetukset"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:13
msgid "Create an account and activate carriers"
msgstr "Luo tili ja aktivoi rahdinkuljettajat"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:15
msgid ""
"To get started, `create or log in to a Sendcloud account <https://"
"account.sendcloud.com/signup/ ?"
"utm_source=odoo&utm_medium=partnerships&utm_campaign=partner_integrations_page>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:18
msgid ""
"On the Sendcloud platform, follow the `Sendcloud integration documentation "
"<https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/360059470491-Odoo-Native-"
"integration>`_ to configure the account and generate the connector "
"credentials."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:23
msgid ""
"For new account creation, Sendcloud will ask for a :abbr:`VAT (Value-Added "
"Tax Identification)` number or :abbr:`EORI (Economic Operators' Registration "
"and Identification)` number. After completing the account setup, activate "
"(or deactivate) the shipping carriers that will be used in the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Uutta tiliä luotaessa Sendcloud pyytää :abbr:`ALV-tunnusta "
"(arvonlisäverorekisteröintitunnus)` tai :abbr:`EORI-numeroa (talouden "
"toimijoiden rekisteröinti- ja tunnistenumero)`. Tilin luomisen jälkeen "
"aktivoi (tai poista käytöstä) kuljetusyhtiöt, joita käytetään Odoo-"
"tietokannassa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:29
msgid ""
"Odoo integration of Sendcloud works on free Sendcloud plans *only* if a bank "
"account is linked, since Sendcloud won't ship for free. To use shipping "
"rules, or individual custom carrier contacts, a paid plan of Sendcloud is "
"**required**."
msgstr ""
"Odoon Sendcloud-integraatio toimii ilmaisilla Sendcloud-paketeilla *vain*, "
"jos pankkitili on linkitetty, koska Sendcloud ei toimita ilmaiseksi. "
"Lähetyssääntöjen tai yksittäisten räätälöityjen kuljetusyhtiökontaktien "
"käyttämiseen **vaaditaan** maksullinen Sendcloud-paketti."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:36
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:183
msgid "Warehouse configuration"
msgstr "Varaston konfigurointi"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:38
msgid ""
"Once logged into the Sendcloud account, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings "
"--> Shipping --> Addresses`, and fill in the field for :guilabel:`Warehouse "
"address`."
msgstr ""
"Kun olet kirjautunut Sendcloud-tilille, siirry kohtaan "
":menuselection:`Asetukset --> Lähetys --> Osoitteet` ja täytä kenttä "
":guilabel:`Varaston osoite`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Adding addresses in the Sendcloud settings."
msgstr "Osoitteiden lisääminen Sendcloudin asetuksissa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:45
msgid ""
"To allow Sendcloud to process returns as well, a :guilabel:`Return Address` "
"is required. Under the :guilabel:`Miscellaneous section`, there is a field "
"called :guilabel:`Address Name (optional)`. The Odoo warehouse name should "
"be entered here, and the characters should be exactly the same."
msgstr ""
"Jotta Sendcloud voi käsitellä myös palautuksia, vaaditaan "
":guilabel:`Palautusosoite`. :guilabel:`Sekalainen-osiossa` on kenttä nimeltä "
":guilabel:`Osoitteen nimi (valinnainen)`. Odoo-varaston nimi tulee syöttää "
"tähän, ja merkkien tulee olla täsmälleen samat."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:0
msgid "**SendClould configuration**"
msgstr "**SendCloud-konfiguraatio**"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Miscellaneous`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Sekalainen`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Address Name (optional)`: `Warehouse #1`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Osoitteen nimi (valinnainen)`: `Warehouse #1`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Brand`: `Default`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Brändi`: `Default`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:0
msgid "**Odoo warehouse configuration**"
msgstr "**Odoo-varaston konfiguraatio**"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Warehouse`: `Warehouse #1`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Varasto`: `Warehouse #1`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Short Name`: `WH`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Lyhyt nimi`: `WH`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Company`: `My company (San Francisco)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Yritys`: `My company (San Francisco)`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Address`: `My Company (San Francisco)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Osoite`: `My Company (San Francisco)`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:62
msgid ""
"Notice how the inputs for the :guilabel:`Warehouse` field, for both the Odoo "
"configuration and the Sendcloud configuration, are the exact same."
msgstr ""
"Huomaa, kuinka :guilabel:`Varasto`-kentän syötteet ovat täsmälleen samat "
"sekä Odoo-konfiguraatiossa että Sendcloud-konfiguraatiossa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:66
msgid "Generate Sendcloud credentials"
msgstr "Sendcloud-tunnusten luominen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:68
msgid ""
"In the Sendcloud account, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Integrations` in the menu on the right. Next, search for :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Native`. Then, click on :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Sendcloud-tilillä siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Asetukset --> Integraatiot` "
"oikean puolen valikossa. Etsi sitten :guilabel:`Odoo Native`. Klikkaa sitten "
":guilabel:`Yhdistä`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:71
msgid ""
"After clicking on :guilabel:`Connect`, the page redirects to "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud API` settings page, where the :guilabel:`Public and "
"Secret Keys` are produced. The next step is to name "
"the :guilabel:`Integration`. The naming convention is as follows: `Odoo "
"CompanyName`, with the user's company name replacing `CompanyName` (e.g. "
"`Odoo StealthyWood`)."
msgstr ""
"Kun on klikattu :guilabel:`Connect`, sivu ohjautuu :guilabel:`Sendcloud "
"API` -asetussivulle, jossa :guilabel:`Public and Secret Keys` luodaan. "
"Seuraava vaihe on nimetä :guilabel:`Integration`. Nimeämiskäytäntö on "
"seuraava: `Odoo YrityksenNimi`, jossa käyttäjän yrityksen nimi korvaa "
"`YrityksenNimi` (esim. `Odoo StealthyWood`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:76
msgid ""
"Then, check the box next to :guilabel:`Service Points` and select the "
"shipping services for this integration. After saving, the :guilabel:`Public "
"and Secret Keys` are generated."
msgstr ""
"Valitse seuraavaksi ruutu :guilabel:`Service Points` -kohdan vierestä ja "
"valitse toimituspalvelut tälle integraatiolle. Tallennuksen jälkeen "
":guilabel:`Public and Secret Keys` luodaan."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Configuring the Sendcloud integration and receiving the credentials."
msgstr ""
"Sendcloud-integraation määrittäminen ja tunnistetietojen vastaanottaminen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:84
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:90
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:158
