#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:195
msgid ""
"Sendcloud does not provide test keys when a company tests the sending of a "
"package in Odoo. This means if a package is created, the configured "
"Sendcloud account will be charged, unless the associated package is canceled "
"within 24 hours of creation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:199
msgid ""
"Odoo has a built-in layer of protection against unwanted charges when using "
"test environments. Within a test environment, if a shipping method is used "
"to create labels, then those labels are immediately canceled after the "
"creation — this occurs automatically. The test and production environment "
"settings can be toggled back and forth from their respective smart buttons."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:207
msgid "Shipping information"
msgstr "Toimitustiedot"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:209
msgid ""
"To use Sendcloud to generate shipping labels, the following information "
"**must** be filled out accurately and completely in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Sendcloudin käyttämiseksi toimituskirjojen luomiseen seuraavat tiedot **on** "
"täytettävä tarkasti ja kokonaan Odoossa:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:212
msgid ""
"**Customer information**: when creating a quotation, ensure the "
"selected :guilabel:`Customer` has a valid phone number, email address, and "
"shipping address."
msgstr ""
"**Asiakastiedot**: tarjousta luotaessa varmista, että valitulla "
":guilabel:`Asiakkaalla` on kelvollinen puhelinnumero, sähköpostiosoite ja "
"toimitusosoite."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:215
msgid ""
"To verify, select the :guilabel:`Customer` field to open their contact page. "
"Here, add their shipping address in the :guilabel:`Contact` field, along "
"with their :guilabel:`Mobile` number and :guilabel:`Email` address."
msgstr ""
"Vahvistaaksesi valitse :guilabel:`Asiakas`-kenttä avataksesi heidän "
"yhteystietosivunsa. Lisää tähän heidän toimitusosoitteensa "
":guilabel:`Yhteystieto`-kenttään yhdessä heidän :guilabel:`Matkapuhelin`-"
"numeronsa ja :guilabel:`Sähköposti`-osoitteensa kanssa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:219
msgid ""
"**Product weight**: ensure all products in an order have a "
"specified :guilabel:`Weight` in the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of their "
"product form. Refer to the :ref:`Product weight section <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` of this article for detailed "
"instructions."
msgstr ""
"**Tuotteen paino**: varmista, että kaikilla tilauksen tuotteilla on "
"määritetty :guilabel:`Paino` niiden tuotelomakkeen :guilabel:`Varastointi`-"
"välilehdellä. Katso yksityiskohtaiset ohjeet tämän artikkelin :ref:`tuotteen "
"paino -osiosta <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-weight>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:223
msgid ""
"**Warehouse address**: ensure the warehouse name and address in Odoo match "
"the :ref:`previously defined warehouse <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-warehouse-config>` in the Sendcloud setup. For details on "
"warehouse configuration in Odoo, refer to the :ref:`warehouse configuration "
"section <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>` of the "
"third-party shipping documentation."
msgstr ""
"**Varaston osoite**: varmista, että varaston nimi ja osoite Odoossa "
"vastaavat Sendcloud-asetuksissa :ref:`aiemmin määritettyä varastoa "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/sendcloud-warehouse-config>`. Katso tiedot "
"varaston määrityksestä Odoossa kolmannen osapuolen toimituksia koskevan "
"dokumentaation :ref:`varaston määritys -osiosta <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:230
msgid "Generate labels with Sendcloud"
msgstr "Luo tarroja Sendcloudilla"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:232
msgid ""
"When creating a quotation in Odoo, add shipping and a :guilabel:`Sendcloud "
"shipping product`. Then, :guilabel:`Validate` the delivery. Shipping label "
"documents are automatically generated in the chatter, which include the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Luotaessa tarjousta Odoossa lisää toimitus ja :guilabel:`Sendcloud-"
"toimitustuote`. Sitten :guilabel:`Vahvista` toimitus. Toimituskirja-"
"asiakirjat luodaan automaattisesti keskusteluun, ja ne sisältävät seuraavat:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:236
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:205
msgid ":guilabel:`Shipping label(s)` depending on the number of packages."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Toimitustarrat` pakettien määrästä riippuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:237
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Return label(s)` if the Sendcloud connector is configured for "
"returns."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Palautustarrat`, jos Sendcloud-liitäntä on määritetty "
"palautuksille."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:238
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customs document(s)` should the destination country require them."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tulliasiakirjat`, jos kohdemaa vaatii niitä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:240
msgid "Additionally, the tracking number is now available."
msgstr "Lisäksi seurantanumero on nyt saatavilla."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:243
msgid ""
"When return labels are created, Sendcloud automatically charges the "
"configured Sendcloud account."
msgstr ""
"Kun palautustarrat luodaan, Sendcloud veloittaa automaattisesti määritetyltä "
"Sendcloud-tililtä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:246
msgid "Shipping rules"
msgstr "Toimitussäännöt"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:248
msgid ""
"Optionally, create shipping rules to automatically generate shipping labels "
"tailored to different product needs. For example, a shipping rule can be "
"created for customers shipping expensive jewelry items to purchase insurance."
msgstr ""
"Vaihtoehtoisesti voit luoda toimitussääntöjä luodaksesi automaattisesti "
"toimituskirjoja, jotka on räätälöity eri tuotteiden tarpeisiin. Esimerkiksi "
"toimitussääntö voidaan luoda asiakkaille, jotka lähettävät kalliita "
"korutuotteita ja haluavat ostaa vakuutuksen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:253
msgid ""
"Shipping rules do **not** affect :ref:`shipping rate calculations <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>`, and are only used to improve the "
"process of :doc:`generating shipping labels <labels>`."
msgstr ""
"Toimitussäännöt **eivät** vaikuta :ref:`toimitusmaksujen laskentaan "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>`, ja niitä käytetään vain "
"parantamaan :doc:`toimituskirjojen luomisprosessia <labels>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:257
msgid ""
"To use shipping rules, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Delivery: Shipping Methods`, and select the intended "
"`Sendcloud` shipping method."
msgstr ""
"Toimitussääntöjen käyttämiseksi siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Varastointi-"
"sovellus --> Asetukset --> Toimitus: Toimitustavat` ja valitse haluamasi "
"`Sendcloud`-toimitustapa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:260
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Configuration` tab, in "
"the :guilabel:`OPTIONS` section, choose the kind of shipments the shipping "
"rules apply to, via the :guilabel:`Use Sendcloud shipping rules` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sendcloud-määritys`-välilehdellä, :guilabel:`ASETUKSET`-osiossa, "
"valitse minkä tyyppisiä lähetyksiä toimitussäännöt koskevat :guilabel:`Käytä "
"Sendcloudin toimitussääntöjä`-kentän kautta."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:264
msgid ""
"From here, choose either: :guilabel:`Shipping` to "
"customers, :guilabel:`Returns` from customers, or :guilabel:`Both`."
msgstr ""
"Valitse tästä joko: :guilabel:`Toimitus` asiakkaille, "
":guilabel:`Palautukset` asiakkailta tai :guilabel:`Molemmat`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Use Shipping Rules field."
msgstr "Käytä toimitussääntöjä -kenttä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:271
msgid ""
"Then, in the Sendcloud website, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Shipping rules`. Create a new shipping rule by clicking :guilabel:`Create "
"New`."
msgstr ""
"Siirry sitten Sendcloud-verkkosivustolla kohtaan "
":menuselection:`Asetukset --> Toimitussäännöt`. Luo uusi toimitussääntö "
"napsauttamalla :guilabel:`Luo uusi`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:274
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Actions` section, set a :guilabel:`Condition` to determine "
"when the rule applies. Then, configure what to do when packages meet the "
"condition."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Toiminnot`-osiossa aseta :guilabel:`Ehto` määrittääksesi, milloin "
"sääntö otetaan käyttöön. Määritä sitten, mitä tehdään, kun paketit täyttävät "
"ehdon."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:278
msgid ""
"`Create shipping rules on Sendcloud <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/ 10274470454292-How-to-create-shipping-rules#examples-smart-"
"shipping-rules>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Vytvoření dopravních pravidel na Sendcloud <https://support.sendcloud.com/"
"hc/en-us/articles/ 10274470454292-How-to-create-shipping-rules#examples-"
"smart-shipping-rules>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:282
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "UKK"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:285
msgid "Shipment is too heavy"
msgstr "Lähetys on liian painava"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:287
msgid ""
"If the shipment is too heavy for the Sendcloud service that is configured, "
"then the weight is split to simulate multiple packages. Products will need "
"to be put in different :guilabel:`Packages` to :guilabel:`Validate` the "
"transfer and generate labels."
msgstr ""
"Jos lähetys on liian painava määritetylle Sendcloud-palvelulle, paino "
"jaetaan simuloimaan useita paketteja. Tuotteet on laitettava eri "
":guilabel:`Paketteihin`, jotta siirto voidaan :guilabel:`Vahvistaa` ja luoda "
"tarrat."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:291
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rules` can also be set up in Sendcloud to use other shipping "
"methods when the weight is too heavy. However, note that these rules will "
"not apply to the shipping price calculation on the calculation on the sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Säännöt` voidaan myös määrittää Sendcloudissa käyttämään muita "
"toimitusmenetelmiä, kun paino on liian suuri. Huomaa kuitenkin, että nämä "
"säännöt eivät vaikuta toimitushinnan laskentaan myyntitilauksessa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:296
msgid "Personal carrier contract"
msgstr "Henkilökohtainen kuljetussopimus"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:298
msgid ""
"Use custom prices from a direct carrier contract, via CSV upload, by first "
"logging into Sendcloud, navigating to :menuselection:`Settings --> Carriers "
"--> My contracts`, and then selecting the intended contract."
msgstr ""
"Käytä mukautettuja hintoja suorasta kuljetussopimuksesta CSV-latauksen "
"kautta kirjautumalla ensin Sendcloudiin, siirtymällä kohtaan "
":menuselection:`Asetukset --> Kuljetusyritykset --> Omat sopimukset` ja "
"valitsemalla sitten haluttu sopimus."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Navigate to the contracts section in Sendcloud."
msgstr "Siirry sopimusosioon Sendcloudissa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:306
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Contract prices` section, click :guilabel:`Download "
"CSV` and fill out the contract prices in the :guilabel:`price` column of the "
"CSV file template."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sopimushinnat`-osiossa napsauta :guilabel:`Lataa CSV` ja täytä "
"sopimushinnat CSV-tiedostomallin :guilabel:`hinta`-sarakkeeseen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:310
msgid ""
"Ensure the CSV file includes the correct prices to avoid any inaccuracies."
msgstr ""
"Varmista, että CSV-tiedosto sisältää oikeat hinnat epätarkkuuksien "
"välttämiseksi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Show sample contract CSV from Sendcloud, highlighting the price column."
msgstr "Näytä Sendcloudin esimerkkisopimusten CSV korostaen hintasaraketta."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:316
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Upload` the completed CSV file to Sendcloud, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save these prices`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lataa` täytetty CSV-tiedosto Sendcloudiin ja napsauta sitten "
":guilabel:`Tallenna nämä hinnat`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:319
msgid ""
"`Sendcloud: How to upload contract prices with carriers <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/5163547066004>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Sendcloud: How to upload contract prices with carriers <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/5163547066004>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:323
msgid "Measuring volumetric weight"
msgstr "Tilavuuspainon mittaaminen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:325
msgid ""
"Many carriers have several measures for weight. There is the actual weight "
"of the products in the parcel, and there is the *volumetric weight* "
"(:dfn:`Volumetric weight is the volume that a package occupies when in "
"transit. In other words it is the physical size of a package`)."
msgstr ""
"Monilla kuljetusyrityksillä on useita painomittoja. On tuotteiden todellinen "
"paino paketissa ja on *tilavuuspaino* (:dfn:`Tilavuuspaino on tila, jonka "
"paketti vie kuljetuksen aikana. Toisin sanoen se on paketin fyysinen koko`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:330
msgid ""
"Check to see if selected carrier(s) already have defined formulas to compute "
"the volumetric weight."
msgstr ""
"Tarkista, onko valituilla kuljetusyrityksillä jo määritettyjä kaavoja "
