msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Manufacture`: valitse, valmistetaanko tuotteet :doc:`yhdessä <../"
"../../manufacturing/basic_setup/one_step_manufacturing>`, :doc:`kahdessa <../"
"../../manufacturing/basic_setup/two_step_manufacturing>` vai :doc:`kolmessa "
"vaiheessa <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/three_step_manufacturing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buy to Resupply`: tick this checkbox to allow for purchased "
