"warehouse's name. If the warehouse can be resupplied by more than one "
"warehouse, make sure to check those warehouses' boxes too. Now, Odoo knows "
"which warehouses can resupply this warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Välilehdellä :guilabel:`Warehouse Configuration` etsi kenttä "
